## Use case

when text is overflow the max height of TextField, select all text will cause the SelectionControls to show at a location far away from the TextField.

the code for this case:
```

import 'dart:ui';

import 'package:flutter/material.dart';

void main() {
  runApp(MyApp());
}

class MyApp extends StatelessWidget {
  // This widget is the root of your application.
