### Steps to reproduce

steps are easy, you just need a Samsung watch with new **One UI 8** (with older versions the keyboard works fine), run a simple flutter app with just a text field.

in the following I click on text field:
<img width="432" height="432" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/bb001d25-3310-40d1-b33a-216f1578e5b1" />

write do but only see d:
<img width="432" height="432" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/90ea3b55-04b8-4966-8a42-5260198212c1" />

click done and see actually do:
