click again on text field and ad es but see nothing:
<img width="432" height="432" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/0118ce0c-2bd8-438c-9dbb-a97c9fc2376c" />

but the text field has it.
<img width="432" height="432" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2760cd4f-f0e0-4689-9120-8f197e8bc6e7" />

You might say it's a keyboard issue, but I tried on store search field and it works fine there.

### Expected results

We expect the keyboard page to be updated with the result of typing for Samsung keyboard

### Actual results

When writing with Samsung Keyboard the first letters appears and the rest is just saved in the controller and not shown on the keyboard view of watch.
when typing you can see the following result in the console:

```
D/InputConnectionAdaptor(25799): The input method toggled text monitoring on
