I/ImeTracker(25799): system_server:6a316ed8: onShown
D/InputConnectionAdaptor(25799): The input method toggled text monitoring off
```
After the monitoring turns off the keyboard is not updated on watch

Note: I tried installing Gboard and it works fine. But the default keyboard on Samsung is Samsung keyboard and it's rare that users would change their keyboard on watch.


